{"id":1706564,"retrievedAt":"2026-06-02T15:13:26.396Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"https://vimeo.com/1165027173","id":1706564,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["BR"],"original_language":"pt","original_title":"Salitre não mais!","overview":"For around fifteen years, I have been filming a forest of imburana de cambão trees that has been progressively disappearing, located on the border between the states of Bahia and Pernambuco. The visual saturation created through image overlaps and the division of the screen into three parts fosters the emergence of a particular rhythm, in which pulsating texts impose other forms of escape.The gradual disappearance of this forest echoes texts evoking the consequences of climate change, while also inscribing fire and logging as human acts contributing to this impoverishment.The basis of this film was the installation of the same name presented as part of an exhibition at the Frans Krajcberg Space in 2025. The film is denser. The imburanas de cambão burst into flames as the sertão turns into desert.","popularity":0,"poster_path":"/xVdjuZZYsqv8xvRKnOnr7QJOHUq.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":300469,"logo_path":null,"name":"yannbeauvais.com","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","name":"Brazil"}],"release_date":"2026-07-04","revenue":0,"runtime":28,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Portuguese","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Salitre no more","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","title":"Salitre no more!","type":""}]},"credits":{"cast":[],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2013794,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Yann Beauvais","original_name":"Yann Beauvais","popularity":0.0453,"profile_path":"/jTAHhdTQziEGqydwy6537mNSPiw.jpg","credit_id":"6a1e22691ef7c3812f